VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT NSPredicate\s*\(\s*format\s*:\s*["'][^"']*%@
WHEN EXPR MISSING:argumentArray|CVarArg|predicateWithValue
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects NSPredicate format strings that interpolate values without using the argument array pattern.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for NSFetchRequest Predicate from User Input.
